(468, 1, '2013-05-27 08:00:29', '2013-05-27 08:00:29', 'So as to ensure that your e-mail communications are received by the respective persons, in particular e-mail communications containing instructions having a deadline, and so as to ensure the deadlines are timely met, please always verify our confirmation of receipt of your instructions in a timely fashion. It is preferable to also send us a confirmation copy of your instructions simultaneous by fax.\r\n\r\n[gravityform id="2" name="Please fill in the form Below"]', 'Career Opportunity at Ehrlich & Fenster', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-6', '', '', '2013-05-27 08:00:29', '2013-05-27 08:00:29', '', 20, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=468', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
