(472, 1, '2013-06-17 13:21:53', '2013-06-17 13:21:53', 'Ehrlich &amp; Fenster is a leading Israel based Patent Attorneys Firm. The Firm specializes in all matters concerning protection and prose- cution of Intellectual Property. For the past several years Ehrlich &amp; Partners was the fastest growing Firm in the field of Intellectual Property in Israel. This significant growth is due to unrivaled knowledge and expertise in all technological fields and due to the personal service rendered to each and every client. The Firm provides Patent, Design, Trademark and Breeder’s Rights services to Corporations, Institu- tions, Governmental Institutes, Universities and Individual clients around the world.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-11', '', '', '2013-06-17 13:21:53', '2013-06-17 13:21:53', '', 11, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=472', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
