n offering yet better and new services.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTwo current  areas of expansion are in the field of Trademarks and services rendered to foreign associates. Ehrlich &amp; Fenster aggressively pursues effective and broad trademark protection for their clients with the Israel Trade Mark Registry, based on an understanding of the client''s business needs.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEhrlich &amp; Fenster Patent Attorneys  also file more PCT applications than any other Israeli patent attorney firm and have a rapidly increasing number  of national phase filings all over the world.', 'Managing IP World Survey 2008 ranks Ehrlich & Fenster as Israel''s No. 1 Patent Attorneys Firm', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '700-revision-2', '', '', '2013-10-16 12:10:13', '2013-10-16 12:10:13', '', 700, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=702', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
